ISLAMABAD, Apr 12 (APP):Central Secretary Information Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf, Farrukh Habib said on Tuesday that the date of public meeting of PTI scheduled for April 23 in the historic ground of Minar-e-Pakistan has been changed view of the day of martyrdom of Hazrat Ali (A.S).
This public meeting will now be held on Sunday, April 24, he said in a tweet.
